# 詞: 睇怕

1. 今日天氣咁凍，睇怕落雨會凍死人。 (The weather is so cold today; I'm afraid it'll rain and get even colder.)
2. 佢今日遲咗成個鐘，睇怕今日唔會返嚟啦。 (He was late by a whole hour today; I'm afraid he won't come back today.)
3. 聽日要考試，睇怕今晚要溫書溫夜啲。 (There's an exam tomorrow; I'm afraid I'll have to study late tonight.)
4. 佢把聲咁沙，睇怕感冒咗呀。 (His voice is so hoarse; I'm afraid he's caught a cold.)
5. 呢排咁多嘢做，睇怕冇時間去旅行。 (There's so much work lately; I'm afraid there's no time to travel.)
6. 佢面色咁差，睇怕身體有啲問題。 (He looks so pale; I'm afraid there's something wrong with his health.)
7. 今晚咁夜，睇怕唔夠時間做完功課。 (It's so late tonight; I'm afraid there won't be enough time to finish the homework.)
8. 個天咁黑，睇怕就嚟落大雨。 (The sky is so dark; I'm afraid it's about to rain heavily.)
9. 佢咁耐都唔覆我，睇怕佢唔想同我做朋友。 (He hasn't replied for so long; I'm afraid he doesn't want to be friends with me.)
10. 聽日要presentation，睇怕要準備多啲嘢。 (There's a presentation tomorrow; I'm afraid I need to prepare more stuff.) [end of text]


